channel.description:
# :broom: [color=amber]Dustpan Deception[/color] :broom: *Hosted by Marluxion*
### [color=amber]Rules[/color] Don't be a jerk Don't gamethrow If I have to prod you more than once, you'll be replaced.
### [color=amber]Gameplay[/color] Days will be 36 hours Nights will be 12 hours Voting is plurality + Majority. Ties will be broken by RNG. The Mafia have one factional kill per night. Any member can perform it. The Mafia have a day and night chat.
### [color=amber]The Setup[/color] [color=red]**2x Mafia Goon**[/color] [color=red]**1x Mafia One-Shot Janitor**[/color] [color=green]**One-Shot Janitor Vigilante**[/color] [color=green]**8x Vanilla Town**[/color]
[details="Rolecards"] > # [color=green]Vanilla Town[/color] > You can't do anything, but you're still amazing!
> # [color=green]One-Shot Janitor Vigilante[/color] > Once per game at night, you make shoot another player. That player's flip will be publicly cleaned. You will be informed of what they were privately.
> # [color=red]Mafia Goon[/color] > The Godfather has ordered you to defeat the townies! At least you've got a janitor around to help clean up the scene.
> # [color=red]Mafia One-Shot Janitor[/color] > Once per game, you may clean the factional kill. Their flip will be publicly cleaned. You will be informed of what they were privately. [/details]
# [color=amber]Players:[/color] 1. ~~Hjasik - Town N4~~ 2. ~~Mercenary - Mafia Lynched D3~~ 3. ~~Ashe - Cleaned N1~~ 4. overthebin 5. Geyde 6. ~~MaximusPrime - Town Lynched D4~~ 7. ~~Wolfy / Mathblade - Town N3~~ 8. ~~Margaret - Cleaned N1~~ 9. ~~Luxy - Mafia Lynched D2~~ 10. ~~Sam17z - Vanilla Town~~ 11. Insanity 12. ~~Livicus - Town - Lynched d1~~
Backups: Margaret, MathBlade
# [color=amber]Shortcuts[/color] :link: [Start of Reroll](https://forum.imperium42.com/t/dustpan-redux-day-1-12-12-alive/73651/362?u=marluxion)
